  "subject": "[DCAE] Revert TLS disabling for external DCAE MSs",
  "commit_message": "[DCAE] Revert TLS disabling for external DCAE MSs\n\nFor Kohn we still base on AAF CM to provide TLS on the external\nDCAE services:\n- dcae-ves-collector\n- dcae-hv-ves-collector\n- dcae-datafile-collector\n- dcae-pm-mapper connection to dmaap-dr-node\nFor London this will be changed to use Ingress TLS\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-2775\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Geissler <andreas-geissler@telekom.de>\nChange-Id: I1deb6492483c6ae2db7b5437319dc722d78727c0\n(cherry picked from commit 3502e73a2762fc50f9ba3ae5d65a3efe5f05bead)\n",
